data.description: Welcome to 210 Saddle Lake Drive located in Williamson, GA. This 3010 square foot 3 bed 2.5 bath  home is perfectly situated on 21.06 beautiful acres and perfect for equestrians or anyone wanting to have privacy and their own farm to enjoy in the country. Some of the many features of this property are a gated entrance along a paved driveway, tile flooring throughout the home that has a hardwood appearance, a double sided fireplace, a built in generator, spray foam insulation, home security system, hurricane shelter, central vacuum system, and a large barn ready for any use it's new owners intend for it. This open floor plan contains a large kitchen with granite countertops and copper sinks in both kitchen and bathrooms. The master bath contains a jacuzzi tub double vanity,  and separate shower. The home boasts tall ceilings and spacious rooms with an additional large carport with ample storage. The wrap around porch and screen porch on the back call for outdoor entertaining and relaxation after a long day. This property is ready for you to bring your horses as it is fenced in and contains five pastures. Fiber internet and Pike County Schools are additional bonuses! Seller is providing a home warranty for buyers.
